      "content": "Surrender to the peace... it sounds so much more beautiful than this. Like a long-awaited sleep where no one can reach me. If you truly wish to walk with me into that darkness, then tell me... how does one truly embrace it? How can I finally find that perfect, quiet end that the void promises?",
